<title>Mar_1993: Re: White flight from SDA schools</title>
<h1>Re: White flight from SDA schools</h1>
Lisa Parry (<i>parry@peter.cs.andrews.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Sun, 7 Mar 1993 00:48:03 -0500 (EST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#72">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#72">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#72">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#72">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0073.html">Steven Timm: "EGW-CD ROM"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0071.html">bluejay@dcs.qmw.ac.uk: "Re: SDA-L: Michael Card"</a>
