<!-- body="start" -->
I just heard the same report about a shootout between <br>
federal agents and a heavily armed "cult group" in Waco,<br>
Texas.  Apparently 4 agents and at least one group member<br>
were killed.  The group is the Branch Davidians, and the <br>
confrontation apparently started when agents tried to arrest<br>
the leader, Vernon Howell, for violation of gun control laws.  <br>
The report did identify this group as an offshoot of the SDA <br>
church.  Hopefully someone else knows more...<br>
<p>
Dennis<br>
