<!-- body="start" -->
After giving info to the list last evening, I went home and watched the<br>
news.  It appears that it was not the Davidian SDA's that were involved<br>
in the shootout, but the Branch Davidians.  This appears to be the group<br>
listed in Melton's encyclopedic work as the Branch SDAs (p. 513), who<br>
have a po address in Waco, TX.  This is merely a splinter of a splinter<br>
(the Davidians, or "Shepherd's Rod").<br>
<p>
Harvey Brenneise<br>
