<title>Mar_1993: Re: Shootout in Texas</title>
<h1>Re: Shootout in Texas</h1>
Woody Baker (<i>woody@knapper.cactus.org</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 01 Mar 1993 08:03:57 CST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#2">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#2">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#2">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#2">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0003.html">CHRMD@cc.newcastle.edu.au: "Re: Shootout in Texas"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0001.html">Harvey Brenneise: "Branch SDA's"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
