work.  I agree with Tony.<br>
How long are we lay people going to leave ministry up to the few?  They<br>
seem to have forgotten that ALL Christians are gifted ministers--or at<br>
least should be.  We the lay people have bought into their understanding<br>
and see ourselves as benchwarmers and givers of offering.  <br>
Nothing is farther from the New Testament truth.<br>
<p>
Yours for a whole church.<br>
Nancy<br>
