<title>Mar_1993: RE: Serving without a degree</title>
<h1>RE: Serving without a degree</h1>
Marcus Stringer (<i>marcuss@microsoft.com</i>)<br>
<i>Tue,  2 Mar 93 09:24:34 PST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#27">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#27">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#27">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#27">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0028.html">Fred Kinsey: "Re: AZ Republic/AP on Howell/Koresh"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0026.html">Steven Timm: "Positive PR in Indianapolis"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
