Hi all,<br>
<p>
Just an update of news coverage over here.<br>
<p>
The weekend papers featured 2 full page articles on this issue. The articles<br>
went into substantial detail regarding the Branch Davidians relationship<br>
with the SDA church. Especially mentioned was Koresh's  prophetic interp. and<br>
how this to some extent was derived from the SDA church.<br>
<p>
The articles also looked at Koresh's life since childhood and mentioned<br>
how he mainly recruited his followers from the SDA church and made two<br>
recruiting trips to Australia.<br>
<p>
<p>
Ruben.<br>
