I have not had the time to follow all the posts on the Waco battle.<br>
So excuse me if this is redundant.<br>
<p>
This week-end I heard an explanation about their guns.  Their philosophy<br>
comes from Ezekiel 9, regarding the man with the writing kit followed<br>
by the five men with destroying weapons.  They start killing at the<br>
alter.  According to the Davidians, they are the killing team and<br>
the SDA GC is the alter at which they are to start.<br>
<p>
If this has already been discussed then email would be appreciated.<br>
Else, can anyone confirm/deny this for SDAnet.<br>
<p>
DaveB<br>
