spends too much time worrying about distinctives.  I believe a conservative<br>
would say that we have left the distinctives and do not follow them enough.<br>
the Liberal would probably say that that is all we talk about.  I guess we<br>
never hear what we want to hear enough, and we always hear too much that which<br>
we do not want to hear.  I guess I would agree that we could spend more time<br>
teaching the basics of CHristian living, but do we spend too much time on<br>
distinctives?<br>
