<h1>Re:  Texas shootout</h1>
Wong Kwai Ying, Library, X6725 (<i>LBASAANN%USTHK.BITNET@bitnet.cc.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 2 Mar 1993 13:38 HKT</i>
<p>
