On Wed, 3 Mar 1993 08:00:07 CET Bohuslav Moucka said:<br>
<i>&gt;Dear networkers,</i><br>
<i>&gt;I saw a messages about a battle between the police and members of church</i><br>
<i>&gt;of David K... in Texas in TV news yesterday. The commentator said that</i><br>
<i>&gt;this church is a branch of SDA. I hope it is a mistake, because</i><br>
<i>&gt;I can not believe that members of SDA can kill policemen.</i><br>
<i>&gt;I hope that people in USA have more information about it.</i><br>
<i>&gt;Can anybody write me</i><br>
<i>&gt;what has that man or church common with SDA or who is it ?</i><br>
