<i>&gt;                                B. Moucka</i><br>
<i>&gt;</i><br>
<i>&gt;--</i><br>
<i>&gt;  Bohuslav Moucka                           Tel: +42 5 757000 ext. 388</i><br>
<i>&gt;  Inst. of Comp. Science, Masaryk U.        FAX: +42 5 750000</i><br>
<i>&gt;  Buresova 20</i><br>
<i>&gt;  CS-60177 Brno, Czech Republic</i><br>
<i>&gt;  BITNET: moucka%ics.muni.cs%csbrmu11.bitnet</i><br>
<i>&gt;  Internet moucka@ics.muni.cs</i><br>
It is my understanding that the Davidian Branch is an off-shoot of the Shepherd<br>
's Rod. The Shepherd's Rod is an off-shoot of the Seventh-day Adventist Church.<br>
They broke away during the first half of this century. One of the Davidian's<br>
stated goals was to stockpile enough arms so they could destroy the SDA's whom<br>
they considered to be apostates and their mission was to destroy the apostates.<br>
Aparently the ATF division (Alcohol, Tobacco and Firearms) of the Federal<br>
Government took exception to the large number of arms they had assembled.<br>
<p>
Please correct me if I am wrong!<br>
<p>
Wil Clarke, La Sierra University, Riverside, CA 92515-8247, USA<br>
