[From Drew Corrigan]<br>
<p>
Earlier I asked about the identity of "E.B.White". Unfortunately my friend<br>
got it wrong - it was Ellen G White who authored the booklet he received in<br>
his mail. His further comments were:<br>
<p>
<i>&gt; After mentioning the pamphlet to a couple of other people here, it appears</i><br>
<i>&gt; that the SDA have blanketed at least the entire province of Nova Scotia</i><br>
<i>&gt; with a bulk mailing of the pamphlet.</i><br>
  [...]<br>
<i>&gt; In any case, it gives me pleasure to see a document containing a lot of</i><br>
<i>&gt; hard-hitting bible-based truth being direct-mailed to all the homes in</i><br>
<i>&gt; the province. The booklet is pretty hard on the Catholic Church however,</i><br>
<i>&gt; and may loose some effectiveness by quickly polarizing anyone who is</i><br>
<i>&gt; sympathetic to Catholicism.</i><br>
<p>
Just clearing up the confusion,<br>
<p>
Drew. <br>
