There's quite a bit of Adventist-bashing going on in bit.listserv.christia<br>
otherwise known as the CHRISTIA mailing list.  I don't normally subscribe<br>
to that list, but I picked it up in a newsreader just to follow this <br>
thread and respond to it.  Anyone who subscribes or reads that list,<br>
I can use help.  It's possible to subscribe by sending <br>
<p>
SUB CHRISTIA Yourname<br>
<p>
to LISTSERV@ASUACAD<br>
<p>
but I wouldn't unless you're a real glutton for traffic--they turn over <br>
60-100 messages a day.<br>
<p>
Steve Timm<br>
