I have heard much discussion about Desmond Ford since joining the church<br>
but have never been able to read anything written by him to make a <br>
personal informed desision about his ideas.  I have always felt it wrong<br>
to judge a persons ideas when taken 4th or 5th hand.  Does anyone<br>
out there know how I can get some information or books written by him<br>
or maybe an adress for his organization.        <br>
<p>
I have heard what Ron Spears and Colin Standish say about his beliefs<br>
but feel that may not be the whole story.<br>
<p>
Thanks in advance<br>
<p>
YHS Russell<br>
