<title>Mar_1993: Australlian elections on Sabbath</title>
<h1>Australlian elections on Sabbath</h1>
Richard Behrens (<i>behrens@cirrus.com</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 12 Mar 93 10:47:19 MST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#124">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#124">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#124">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#124">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0125.html">TANG BENG YONG: "Pacifism and the church"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0123.html">Harvey Brenneise: "Wedding rings"</a>
