</ul>
<!-- body="start" -->
     I heard on the radio yesterday that there will be elections in<br>
Australia this Saturday.  Not only that, but voting is manditory<br>
($20 fine if you don't vote).  What do you think about voting on<br>
Sabbath?  Also, perhaps someone down under could tell us whether<br>
or not there is ample opportunity to do your voting during non-Sabbath<br>
hours?<br>
<p>
-- Rick Behrens<br>
   Boulder, Colorado<br>
