I just got this report of the fire at the Frederick, MD church which<br>
Carlos Medley mentioned on Sunday.<br>
<p>
The fire at the Fredrick church caused an estimated $3,000,000 damage.<br>
The cause is unknown. The newer school building was not significantly<br>
damaged. The sanctuary and SS classrooms were a total loss.<br>
<p>
