There has been discussion about new covenant and law of freedom <br>
in Finnish newsgroup.  I'm not (now) asking what includes law of<br>
love, which we can find also from old testament (Deut. 6:5,...).<br>
My question is now when law was given first time and where bible<br>
tells it.  As I remember EGW has written that law (= ten commandments)<br>
was given (at least known) before Sinai.  Of course there must have been<br>
law before that as sin has existed.  Some refers to Noachdic laws or<br>
something else (which has not much place in the adventist interpretation, <br>
I suppose).<br>
<p>
<p>
	Juha<br>
