celebrate their role<br>
as a stewards in this earth by voting.  Remember, this is _our_ Father's world.<br>
<p>
If the latter, then we should pose more questions.<br>
<p>
	What did the believers do?  Did they write the president, or<br>
	their political leaders to have the option of voting on another day?<br>
	If nothing, why?<br>
