might happen next.  Also, I see a proper understanding as enchancing to<br>
faith when the events occur and it could act against possible deception<br>
(particularlly in the area of how the second coming occurs) as events come<br>
to a climax.  Of course, this is a limited view of prophecy.  If we look<br>
at EGW we see relevance in the area of enhancing our understanding of the<br>
Scriptures and reminding us of issues in the Bible we might have<br>
overlooked.  I hope this is helpful.  Ian. <br>
