are forbidden, are those of scavengers/carnivors.  Both classes of animals<br>
concentrate toxins, and deseases.  After the flood, GOD allowed the<br>
eating of meat because apparently there was little vegetation left, and<br>
he knew it would shorten sinful man's life span.<br>
