<!-- body="start" -->
We have about six members who have joined SDA-L this month.  If you would<br>
please post to the net and let us know who you are, so we can include<br>
you in the directory, we'd appreciate it much.<br>
<p>
Welcome and enjoy your stay.<br>
<p>
PS:  SDA-L is unmoderated, but that also means it has no agitator<br>
to stir up traffic when traffic is low.  So if you want to see more messages<br>
on SDA-L, post more.<br>
<p>
Steve Timm<br>
Listowner for subscription services<br>
