Steve:<br>
<p>
Here is bio info on me. I'm not really sure what all is wanted<br>
so pick out those parts consistent with the other entries &amp;<br>
skip the rest.<br>
<p>
Rich Hannon, age 44, married 23 yrs, wife Sherri (Rhino).<br>
3 kids - Chris (13), Justin (11), Eric (5). Graduated BS<br>
Chemistry Andrews U 1970, MS Computer Science Michigan State U<br>
1973. Current position - Staff Programmer Unisys. 15 yrs with<br>
the company. Moved to Salt Lake City in 1976. Current technical<br>
involvement - X Windows, Motif, OLTP (On Line Transaction<br>
Processing), DSM (distributed Systems Management). Our organization<br>
is part of Unisys's Unix Systems Group. <br>
<p>
Church activity - member since 1973. Local church jobs - most everything<br>
at one time or another, additional involvement: Conference Committee,<br>
Union Committee, Pacific Union Restructure Committee.<br>
