I don't know much about the type of people that Koresh recruited. It may be<br>
that many of them believed that the SDA church was Babylon. I am convinced<br>
however, that not everyone with Koresh was of that mode. The person I know<br>
who is over there at the moment, Nicole (her twin brother Peter having now<br>
been reported as shot in the earlier round of firing) was never that sort<br>
of person as far as I was aware. I understood her to be serious about<br>
religion, and insightful perhaps, but I never associated her with those<br>
that were especially critical of the church. That is only one of many though.<br>
<p>
