Yes, I do have a question for you Paul.<br>
<p>
You say you definitely do not wish to be classified as a pacifist. How<br>
would you describe a pacifist? <br>
<p>
As I said in a previous post, I would have thought a person could be<br>
"pro-peace" and "anti-war", and yet still agree to serve in the military,<br>
since there are other ills worse than war, such as persecution and <br>
oppression. When I said I though most Christians would classify themselves<br>
as pacifists, I meant "pro-peace" and "anti-war".<br>
<p>
Tony<br>
