Well, if a man has earrings in both ears, it depends on how many<br>
earrings, and on which ear.  As long as a man has one more earring on<br>
his left ear, he is considered straight.  But if even numbers on both<br>
ears or more earrings on his right ear, he is supposed to be gay (of<br>
course, there are wierd people out there, so watch out for those few<br>
exceptions to the rule :-D).  <br>
