<title>Mar_1993: Re: "A Physicist can do anything"</title>
<h1>Re: "A Physicist can do anything"</h1>
Malcolm Butler (<i>malb@boojum.ee.uts.edu.au</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 17 Mar 93 14:50:31 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#197">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#197">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#197">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#197">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0198.html">Steven Timm: "Re: "A Physicist can do anything""</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0196.html">Steven Timm: "Re:  The nature of Christ"</a>
