<title>Mar_1993: Ron Wyatt</title>
<h1>Ron Wyatt</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 18 Mar 1993 21:08:53 -0500 (EST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#206">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#206">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#206">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#206">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0207.html">Steven Timm: "Re: In the presence of alcohol consumption"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0205.html">Malachi Robertson: "anti posts"</a>
