<title>Mar_1993: SDA Yearbook</title>
<h1>SDA Yearbook</h1>
Nancy Vyhmeister (<i>vyhmeist@edmund.cs.andrews.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Sun, 21 Mar 1993 10:40:02 -0500 (EST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#214">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#214">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#214">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#214">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0215.html">Malachi Robertson: "Gentry"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0213.html">David Plaisted: "Syracuse New York"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
</ul>
<!-- body="start" -->
The SDA Yearbook contains names and addresses of church organizations such<br>
as the GC, divisions, unions, and conferences.  Only fully-funded church<br>
institutions are listed under educational, medical, or publishing institu-<br>
tions.  Churches are not listed at all.  Neither are self-supporting<br>
institutions.<br>
<p>
Nancy<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
<p>
