<h1>Bob Gentry  was Re: Ron Wyatt</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Sun, 21 Mar 1993 10:30:23 -0500 (EST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#216">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#216">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#216">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#216">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0217.html">Woody Baker: "Re: NAC C 47 10"</a>
