I am trying to grab the attention of the owner of this list<br>
in order to have my name removed. I seem to experience<br>
some difficulty when trying to unsubscribe. I do not recall<br>
when I was given a "signoff password" which I am supposed to<br>
use to achieve that objective. If you could please assist me<br>
by either refreshing my memory on this password issue or<br>
scratching my name from the list.<br>
Thanks much!<br>
