<title>Mar_1993: Bible Translations</title>
<h1>Bible Translations</h1>
Nancy Vyhmeister (<i>vyhmeist@edmund.cs.andrews.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 19 Mar 1993 09:08:18 -0500 (EST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#241">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#241">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#241">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#241">[ author ]</a>
