<!-- body="start" -->
I read some of the discussion on the Christia mailing list.  One Adventist<br>
said that Adventists do not believe Jesus can live perfectly in you.  I do not<br>
believe that is a true statement.  Some adventists believe that and some<br>
adventists do not.  I did not want to question the statement on that general<br>
mailing list because I did not think it was the place or the time to have<br>
adventists disputing one another.<br>
<p>
I, for one, do not believe that Christ in the believer is folly.<br>
<p>
thank you<br>
