<title>Mar_1993: Why the SDA church needs conservatives</title>
<h1>Why the SDA church needs conservatives</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 26 Mar 1993 17:46:55 -0500 (EST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#287">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#287">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#287">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#287">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0288.html">davidbu@loowit.wr.tek.com: "Re: Why the SDA church needs liberals"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0286.html">Terry L Anderson 908-580-4428: "Adventist thought &amp; Spectrum"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
</ul>
<!-- body="start" -->
There have been many times in the course of SDAnet where I have thought <br>
a position was unsupportable, or perhaps didn't know the reason behind<br>
a particular interpretation.  Time after time people have come through and <br>
shown that there is scriptural backing or historical evidence or both for a<br>
particular position.  While the liberals are trying to point out that our <br>
faith would still stand even if a particular point of interpretation<br>
were not true, the conservatives march ahead and show that is true. <br>
Biblical <br>
Archeology is not dominated by those considered conservative in the SDA<br>
church, but those archeologists who have maintained belief in the truth<br>
of the Bible continue to find evidence of its authenticity.<br>
<p>
Sometimes theirs is a thankless task, witness Wieland and Short who had to<br>
pound away for twenty years or more before they got any attention, and<br>
then it was an attack.  (It's interesting that in 1888 Waggoner and<br>
Jones were considered "Liberals" by the establishment of the time.  What<br>
does this say<br>
about the direction of the motion of the establishment?)<br>
<p>
Fortunately, the structure of the SDA church is that if you have a conviction<br>
about truth, and shout loudly enough for long enough, some people will look<br>
past the messenger to the message, and listen.  Conservatives, please keep <br>
shouting!  We love you, PROOF BY CAPS LOCK and all.<br>
<p>
Steve Timm<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
<p>
