SDA-L and SDAnet membership information as of Mar 25 1993<br>
<p>
This information is for SDA-L and SDAnet members usage only.  Misuse will<br>
not be tolerated.<br>
<p>
152 working addresses are signed up to SDAnet right now, and 42 other working<br>
addresses are signed up to SDA-L but not SDAnet.  17 are signed up to<br>
the SDAnet Digest.  Those who have signed off the lists have been deleted<br>
from the directory, as have those who requested not to be listed.<br>
<p>
Any directory changes or questions about either list should go to me.<br>
