<title>Mar_1993: Re: Why the SDA church needs liberals</title>
<h1>Re: Why the SDA church needs liberals</h1>
Paul Gates (<i>70516.420@compuserve.com</i>)<br>
<i>26 Mar 93 23:51:30 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
