Dave, I agree with you about the liberality of discussion on the SDA net. I <br>
pastor a small church (65 members) . We have 2 SS classes, one that leans <br>
to Conserv. and another class we call the collegiate class where anything <br>
goes! I am a member of the collegiate class and we want the class members <br>
to feel that they can express themselves without being labeled if you know <br>
what I mean!<br>
<p>
I do not think this is a bad thing because several members of the class has <br>
indicated that their relationship (christian experience) has really grown.<br>
<p>
...........Paul<br>
