<title>Mar_1993: Baptism</title>
<h1>Baptism</h1>
Paul Gates (<i>70516.420@compuserve.com</i>)<br>
<i>26 Mar 93 23:51:25 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#308">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#308">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#308">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#308">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0309.html">TANG BENG YONG: "Re:  Toads"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0307.html">Cam Litvin: "Re: Baptism"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
