Baptismal vows have been prepared in different ways in different places.<br>
The ones in use in the Philippines added a promise to attend church Sabbath,<br>
Wednesday, and Friday.  It also had a line about promising to not marry an<br>
outsider.  I asked where they got that.  Everyone seemed to think that was<br>
the normal vow worldwide...  Adaptation--part of mission.<br>
<p>
Nancy<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
