<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0021.html">Harvey Brenneise: "Sodom and Gomorrah"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
</ul>
<!-- body="start" -->
I should think that it would be perfectly alright to restrict underage<br>
students accesses to certain newsgroups.<br>
Cheers<br>
Woody<br>
