<title>May_1993: What was the Pelagian "heresy"?</title>
<h1>What was the Pelagian "heresy"?</h1>
Fred Christiansen (<i>fredch@quad4.phx.mcd.mot.com</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 4 May 93 17:18:20 MST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#43">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#43">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#43">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#43">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0044.html">AAGAARD%morekypr.BITNET@bitnet.cc.cmu.edu: "Des Ford and firm no"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0042.html">Bruce Holm: "May 3 and Portland, OR"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
