<title>May_1993: Koresh.</title>
<h1>Koresh.</h1>
Noe Torres | ECISD (<i>noe@tenet.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 5 May 1993 07:46:41 -0500 (CDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#29">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#29">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#29">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#29">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0030.html">Bill Nickless: "Re: WWC and Internet News"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0028.html">Marcus Stringer: "Re:  Midrash and the Jesus Generation"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
