<h1>Re:  Midrash and the Jesus Generation</h1>
TANG BENG YONG (<i>med10014@nusunix2.nus.sg</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 5 May 93 13:33:27 +0800</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#24">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#24">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#24">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#24">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0025.html">TANG BENG YONG: "Re: Prayer request"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0023.html">Steven Timm: "Midrash and the Jesus Generation"</a>
<li> <b>Maybe in reply to:</b> <a href="0023.html">Steven Timm: "Midrash and the Jesus Generation"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
<li> <b>Next in thread:</b> <a href="0026.html">TANG BENG YONG: "Re:  Midrash and the Jesus Generation"</a>
