<title>May_1993: "Christianity in the life of the young professional"</title>
<h1>"Christianity in the life of the young professional"</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Sun,  9 May 1993 20:57:05 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#51">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#51">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#51">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#51">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0052.html">a11111arne@attmail.com: "Re: WWC and Internet News"</a>
