<title>May_1993: Re: Uniformity and success</title>
<h1>Re: Uniformity and success</h1>
Malcolm Butler (<i>malb@boojum.ee.uts.edu.au</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 13 May 93 15:15:12 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#81">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#81">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#81">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#81">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0082.html">Steven Timm: "Re: E-mail addresses"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0080.html">Fred Christiansen: "Re: Adult Children Of God"</a>
<li> <b>In reply to:</b> <a href="0064.html">Steven Timm: "Uniformity and success"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
