The classic text is Romans 1:26-7 which reads as follows in the NIV:<br>
<p>
"Because of this, God gave them over to shameful lusts.  Even their women<br>
exchanged natural relations for unnatural ones.  In the same way the men<br>
also abandoned natural relations with women and were inflamed with lust<br>
for one another.  Men committed indecent acts with other men, and received<br>
in themselves the due penalty for their perversion."<br>
<p>
As for the legality of homosexual marriages, I am not familiar with the<br>
situation in Hawaii, but in California, not only have homosexual marriages<br>
been legal for some time, they are currently more "politically correct"<br>
than heterosexual marriages.  To me, this is simply one more sign of the<br>
times.<br>
<p>
