side you stay of a (man made) line somewhere in the Pacific. Then there is the<br>
question about places on the other side of the polarcircles, where you could have the <br>
have the sabbath the whole summer or winter, but ehre some commitee has decided to keep it from sdix t<br>
to keep it from six to six.<br>
