word of God."  But, "How do I allow Christ to live out His principles and<br>
character in me towards homosexuals or any other 'condemned'?"<br>
Is it through oppression, prejudice, bigotry, self-righteousness?<br>
Or furthermore, "%WILL% I allow Christ to do it?"<br>
