<title>May_1993: Re: Homosexuality in the Bible</title>
<h1>Re: Homosexuality in the Bible</h1>
<i>CHURMS@nacdh4.nac.ac.za</i><br>
<i>17 May 1993 11:52:23 +0200</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#114">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#114">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#114">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#114">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0115.html">Maurice George Ashton: "Integrated Faith and Learning"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0113.html">Malachi Robertson: "OT Laws and You"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
