<title>May_1993: More Thoughts....</title>
<h1>More Thoughts....</h1>
Marcus Stringer (<i>marcuss@microsoft.com</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 17 May 93 18:48:16 PDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#139">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#139">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#139">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#139">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0140.html">Healy, Tammy R: "organ sizes"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0138.html">TANG BENG YONG: "Re:  female homosexuality in the bible?"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
