<title>May_1993: Re: female homosexuality in the bible?</title>
<h1>Re: female homosexuality in the bible?</h1>
Gingerlei Tupito (<i>tupito@edmund.cs.andrews.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 18 May 1993 09:20:07 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#127">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#127">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#127">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#127">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0128.html">Tom Zirkle: "Re: SDA world mission"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0126.html">Harvey Brenneise: "Re: SDA world mission"</a>
<li> <b>In reply to:</b> <a href="0083.html">TANG BENG YONG: "female homosexuality in the bible?"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
</ul>
<!-- body="start" -->
Beng, this is a reply for your message.  I appreciate your concern about<br>
the homosexual pastor and his claiming that the Bible doesn't mention<br>
anything about homosexual and lesbian, and that you did not find anything<br>
or text in the Bible that talks about that.  First we have to realize that<br>
not everything specific you look for and need to find answers to will be<br>
specifically mention in the Bible.<br>
<p>
The Bible is not an encyclopedia or dictionary, but a book of principles<br>
that you can choose to apply, and to understand it, one must prayerfully<br>
meditate and study with the guidance of the Holy Spirit in order to know<br>
and understnad the will of God in any specific situation we deal with.<br>
<p>
Remember, God created Adam &amp; Eve not Eve &amp; Racheal or Adam &amp; Michael!  He<br>
created a man &amp; a woman (Adam &amp; Eve) and gve them beautiful children - the<br>
kind of family God wants us to be.  If God tells us specifically all<br>
things in details that He does not approve of, the Bible would have been 4<br>
or 5 times or even bigger than it is now!<br>
<p>
Here are some texts that can help you understand and study them<br>
prayerfully so you can understand and be able to share with the homosexual<br>
pastor.  I am not a pastor, but I study God's Word prayerfully and the<br>
Spirit of Prophecy, and without the Holy Spirit's guidance I cannot<br>
understand it.<br>
<p>
1.  GENESIS 1:26&amp;27:  "Then God said, Let us make man; man and maid did he<br>
make them.  And God blessed them and told them, multiply and fill the<br>
earth and subdue it; you are masters of the fish and the birds and all the<br>
animals.<br>
<p>
2.  JUDGES 19:22:  "Just as they were beginning to warm to the occasion, a<br>
gang of sex perverts gathered around the house and began beating at the<br>
door and yelling at the old man to bring out the man who was staying with<br>
him, so they could rape him. (23) The old man stepped outside to talk to<br>
them, "No, my brothers, don't do such a distardly act," he begged, "for he<br>
is my guest." (24) "Here, take my virgin daughter and this man's wife. <br>
I'll bring them out and you can do whatever you like to them--but don't do<br>
such a thing to this man." (25) But they wouldn't listen to him.  Then the<br>
girl's husband pushed her out to them, and they abused her all night,<br>
taking turns raping her until morning."  BENG, PLEASE READ THE WHOLE<br>
CHAPTER SO YOU CAN UNDERSTAND WHAT WAS GOING ON!<br>
<p>
3.  ROMANS 1:26-27 (18-32):  "That's why God let go of them and let them<br>
do all these evil things, so that even THEIR WOMEN TURNED AGAINST GOD'S<br>
NATURAL PLAN FOR THEM AND INDULGED IN SEX SIN WITH EACH OTHER.  (27) And<br>
the MEN, INSTEAD OF HAVING A NORMAN SEX RELATIONSHIP WITH WOMEN, BURNED<br>
WITH LUST FOR EACH OTHER, MEN DOING SHAMEFUL THINGS WITH OTHER MEN AND, AS<br>
A RESULT, GETTING PAID WITHIN THEIR OWN SOULS WITH THE PENALTY THEY SO<br>
RICHLY DESERVED.<br>
<p>
VERSE 18-32:  "But God shows his anger from haeaven agianst all sinful<br>
evil men who push away the truth from them.  (19) For the truth about God<br>
is known to them instinctively, God has put this knowledge in their<br>
hearts.  NOTE:  PLEASE READ ON....<br>
<p>
One more thing you cna mention to this pastor:  God created animals and<br>
from the beginning to tis day, animals alwasy have to be opposite sex in<br>
order to produce a family, NEVER THE SAME SEX!<br>
<p>
I suggest that you fast and pray and ask for God's guidance before you  <br>
talk with with pastor again.  I will pray for you and let us continue to<br>
witness for God with love and compassion and a willingness to win a soul<br>
to Christ.  God loves Homosexuals but he condemned the practice and the<br>
sinfulness involved in it.  Les us pray for them all.  Until then, have a<br>
wonderful day, God bless everyone who have excess with this message!<br>
<p>
Gingerlei Tupito<br>
Staff, James White Libray<br>
Andrews University<br>
