<!-- body="start" -->
Hi,<br>
	I think a simple rule of thumb as to what to do on Sabbath might be:<br>
"does it bring me closer to God?" Obviously, doing things for worldly gain,<br>
to get ahead in the world, are out, as are things which distract us from the<br>
things of God. The Sabbath should be spent in an attitude of prayer and<br>
contemplation of God, everything that gets in the way should be laid aside.<br>
Just a thought,<br>
		beng<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
