<h1>Please post</h1>
GRUMLING   DENNIS   (<i>LIBDKG@orion.depaul.edu</i>)<br>
<i>18 May 93 14:46:00 CST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#125">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#125">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#125">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#125">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0126.html">Harvey Brenneise: "Re: SDA world mission"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0124.html">Marcus Stringer: "RE: The White Lie, golf at PUC, Newbury Park shopping mall"</a>
