Marcus,<br>
<p>
I got it...read it over and it's very much like Sue..as well as myself.<br>
The idea of not judging but listening and trying to help a person who is<br>
struggling with the concept of being homosexual is something Christ would've<br>
done--if ya were to take the Falwellian view--Christ should've jumped up,when<br>
Mary Magdalene was wiping His feet,and said 'Get this whore away--she is an<br>
abomination to me--I don't care WHAT she says about Me changing her life!<br>
She practices a horrible lifestyle and is condemned to death and eternal<br>
damnation!'<br>
<p>
Doesn't quite sound like the Lord I know and love,does it????<br>
<p>
Cheers!<br>
