<title>May_1993: FW:  female homosexuality in the bible?</title>
<h1>FW:  female homosexuality in the bible?</h1>
Marcus Stringer (<i>marcuss@microsoft.com</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 20 May 93 17:32:34 PDT </i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#238">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#238">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#238">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#238">[ author ]</a>
