<i>&gt; </i><br>
<i>&gt; [From John Ash]</i><br>
<i>&gt; Hi all,</i><br>
<i>&gt; </i><br>
<i>&gt;    Well, no longer is there uncensored reading of newsgroups at WWC.  </i><br>
<i>&gt; Evidently the administration finally got wind of all the "evils" which were</i><br>
<i>&gt; available and made a quick &amp; decisive cut.  Here is the notice which was</i><br>
<i>&gt; posted:</i><br>
<i>&gt; </i><br>
<i>&gt; </i><br>
<i>&gt; &gt; By order of C. Michael Bell and President Andreasen, the following</i><br>
<i>&gt; newsgroups </i><br>
<i>&gt; &gt;   are no longer received on this campus.</i><br>
<i>&gt; &gt; </i><br>
<i>&gt; &gt; alt.politics.homosexuality</i><br>
<i>&gt; &gt; alt.sex</i><br>
<i>&gt; &gt; alt.sex.bondage</i><br>
<i>&gt; &gt; alt.sex.motss</i><br>
<i>&gt; &gt; alt.sex.movies</i><br>
<i>&gt; &gt; alt.sex.stories</i><br>
<i>&gt; &gt; alt.sexual.abuse.recovery</i><br>
<i>&gt; &gt; alt.sexual.abuse.recovery.d</i><br>
