<title>May_1993: Re: Bible and Homosexuality (fwd)</title>
<h1>Re: Bible and Homosexuality (fwd)</h1>
Harvey Brenneise (<i>brneise@edmund.cs.andrews.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 21 May 1993 16:05:48 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#220">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#220">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#220">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#220">[ author ]</a>
