[Our list was banned from all Fermilab computers two years back because<br>
somebody did a global search on the word "pornography" and we happened <br>
to be discussing it that week.  At that time I stored all the archives<br>
at Fermilab, which turned out to be one of the illegal activities for<br>
government computers.  SCT]<br>
